                            <comment id="12839252" author="cbradford" created="Sat, 27 Feb 2010 14:28:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added an override for close() in FsShell.TextRecordInputStream that closes the SequenceFile.Reader instance.  I didn&apos;t create new tests because I don&apos;t know the best way to force too many open file handles on the test machine.  However, with this patch I can set ulimit -n 100 and still use the -text option on a path glob with 1000+ files.  Without the patch, files fail to open at the 95th part.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
